Class LocalMatching

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inria.lille.shexjava.validation.LocalMatching
  • public class LocalMatching
extends Object
    Data structure. Similarly to PreMatching, defines a tri-partition of a set of triples. Unlike PreMatching, the matched triples are given as a list of {@link Pair<{@link Triple}, Label>}.
